1
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:28,140
[Whispers of Fate]

2
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:29,950
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,240
What's going on?

4
00:01:52,380 --> 00:01:53,780
Aren't you scared at all?

5
00:01:54,630 --> 00:01:56,070
Lici, are you really that silly?

6
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,870
Don't you even understand fear?

7
00:01:58,570 --> 00:02:00,280
Forget it. You wouldn't understand anyway.

8
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,740
But there is a kind of sound

9
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:04,940
that you can feel
even if you don't understand.

10
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:15,780
What is this?

11
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,830
Can I try too?

12
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,560
This is called music.

13
00:02:23,829 --> 00:02:24,160
Here.

14
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:25,600
Try it.

15
00:03:01,329 --> 00:03:02,790
I know what would suit you.

16
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:04,760
Senior has hidden a Mindfast Fox-Dragon.

17
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,830
I'll find it for you now.

18
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,360
Let's go.

19
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:09,080
What is the Mindfast Fox-Dragon?

20
00:03:09,770 --> 00:03:10,970
It's a real treasure,

21
00:03:11,410 --> 00:03:13,220
a flute that's very difficult to master.

22
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:15,290
What's a flute?

23
00:03:19,450 --> 00:03:20,380
Dinner's ready.

24
00:03:24,850 --> 00:03:26,230
Don't growl at me, little monster.

25
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:26,960
Come with me.

26
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,170
Fang Zhou's heart crystal

27
00:03:39,060 --> 00:03:40,500
is now inside my body,

28
00:03:41,850 --> 00:03:42,690
and his body

29
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,900
has been hidden by me in Zhoudi Tower,

30
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,470
preserved in the Immortal Crystal Coffin

31
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,010
[Fang Zhou's Tomb]

32
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,600
of the Biluo Palace.

33
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,060
His spiritual essence

34
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,520
and vitality are intact.

35
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:54,140
As long as I use the Rebirth Scroll

36
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:55,190
to restore it.

37
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,510
Tang Lici.

38
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,560
I'm such a fool.

39
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:17,700
I actually wanted to trust you again.

40
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,360
[Zhoudi Tower]

41
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,750
♪ Master ♪

42
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:56,890
♪ You failed to take the Biluo Palace ♪

43
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:01,390
♪ And couldn't kill Tang Lici ♪

44
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:06,560
♪ How dare you go back to your old home? ♪

45
00:05:06,810 --> 00:05:08,000
You really don't take

46
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,430
the Fengliu Shop seriously anymore.

47
00:05:09,430 --> 00:05:10,830
I was only gone for 2 days.

48
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:13,660
Can't the Fengliu Shop stay in business
anymore?

49
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:15,240
Master, since your disappearance,

50
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,370
the Sword Alliance
has made thorough preparations.

51
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:18,660
Tang Lici has become

52
00:05:18,690 --> 00:05:20,650
the Guest of Honor of the Sword Alliance.

53
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:22,380
He didn't lose his reputation.

54
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:23,950
Instead, he's become

55
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,480
the most famous marital artist

56
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,280
in the current martial arts world.

57
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:28,950
He's significantly strengthened
the Sword Alliance,

58
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,920
enabling it to amass sufficient fame,
fortune, and influence.

59
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,830
He also has a group of

60
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:33,430
friends willing to die protecting him.

61
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,760
He's now second to none.

62
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,080
But you are

63
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:37,830
notorious in the martial arts world

64
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,690
as the Master of the Fengliu Shop,

65
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,870
bringing shame to Zhoudi Tower.

66
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,630
Leader, do you really think

67
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:49,890
Tang Lici is helping the Sword Alliance?

68
00:05:50,409 --> 00:05:51,270
You're sworn enemies.

69
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,870
You can certainly see through him.

70
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:53,680
His next move

71
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,070
is already clear to you.

72
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,480
Tang Lici is merely

73
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,480
using these fools

74
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,040
to deal with the Fengliu Shop.

75
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,120
He wants them to be

76
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:02,270
his pawns and scapegoats,

77
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,000
paving his way to hell.

78
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:06,750
If Tang Lici can use the Sword Alliance,

79
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,920
you can also use me to kill him.

80
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,800
You think I can't kill him?

81
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,920
He is a true monster,

82
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,560
while you're not yet one.

83
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,720
That's why

84
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,510
you can't kill Tang Lici.

85
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,750
You don't do enough good
to be truly virtuous,

86
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,750
nor can you commit great evil.

87
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:25,680
Yan,

88
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:27,480
with your personality,

89
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,240
you can never reach
the extremes of good or evil.

90
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,950
In the end,

91
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:32,390
you're destined to accomplish nothing.

92
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:34,720
Only I can kill Tang Lici!

93
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:36,590
Whoever touches him,

94
00:06:37,610 --> 00:06:38,930
I will kill them.

95
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:42,650
As you wish.

96
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:02,790
Master.

97
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,200
I finally found you.

98
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,120
I'm so worried about you.

99
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:09,890
Summon everyone to see me.

100
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:29,380
Hidden-Wing Curse Bug.

101
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:30,960
Using it as eyes and ears

102
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:32,970
for searching and scouting.

103
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:35,890
What is Liu Yan looking for?

104
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:38,090
Why did he suddenly

105
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:40,200
return to Zhoudi Tower?

106
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,480
Why overthink it?

107
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,270
Let's investigate this Zhoudi Tower,

108
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,330
and we'll find out.

109
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:51,530
If Liu Yan can't track things down

110
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:53,330
with the Hidden-Wing Curse Bug,

111
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,020
I can't find anything either.

112
00:07:55,030 --> 00:07:57,000
Of course, we need
to ask the puppetry master

113
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,600
Qiaoyi Qiankun to investigate.

114
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,510
He attacked the Biluo Palace

115
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:01,770
by using up a Sky-Fallen Stone fragment.

116
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,270
He can't continue his research.

117
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:04,820
Now, apart from the Biluo Palace,

118
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:06,880
only Puti Valley
possesses Sky-Fallen Stones.

119
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:08,000
If you give him another one,

120
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,930
he'll be eternally grateful to you

121
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,360
and willing to do anything.

122
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:13,800
You're right.

123
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,490
I can't believe
I had to remind you of this.

124
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,640
What a fool.

125
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:19,870
You may leave.

126
00:08:29,030 --> 00:08:31,070
For what happened in the Qingyang Realm,

127
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,470
thank you, Master Puzhu.

128
00:08:33,710 --> 00:08:35,110
I am willing to cooperate

129
00:08:35,310 --> 00:08:36,750
because the Sword Alliance truly

130
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,809
needs Mr. Tang now.

131
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,240
Yielding to circumstances

132
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,150
doesn't mean

133
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,549
I agree with

134
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,679
Mr. Tang's methods.

135
00:08:42,850 --> 00:08:43,480
Same here.

136
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,960
Whatever works is a good strategy.

137
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,080
Why would I need

138
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,000
your approval?

139
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,630
Using money to buy loyalty

140
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,460
is not a good start.

141
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,710
Without any benefit,

142
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,120
you expect those disciples

143
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,600
to risk their lives fighting evil.

144
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,320
Is that fair?

145
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,370
Using profit as bait

146
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:01,630
will lead to betrayal for profit.

147
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,050
The Evil Pill spreads its poison

148
00:09:03,050 --> 00:09:04,770
precisely because of human greed

149
00:09:04,770 --> 00:09:06,700
and delusions of instant success.

150
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,690
Pursuing benefits and avoiding harm

151
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,900
is human nature.

152
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,910
Isn't it a bit harsh

153
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:16,240
to hold ordinary people

154
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,480
to a sage's standard?

155
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:27,200
This is what they call,
"With great rewards

156
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,130
come brave men."

157
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,550
After the news has gotten out,

158
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,910
many sects want to join

159
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:34,030
the Sword Alliance's campaign
against the Fengliu Shop.

160
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:34,720
Moreover,

161
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,480
with the court
and the Biluo Palace's support,

162
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:40,080
the entire Sword Alliance's morale
has soared.

163
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,010
I think we should

164
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,790
take advantage while people are willing

165
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:45,080
to fully eliminate
all Fengliu Shop strongholds.

166
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,480
I've already sent Chunji

167
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,210
to lead a reconnaissance team.

168
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:49,670
Master Cheng,

169
00:09:49,910 --> 00:09:51,110
what's your opinion?

170
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:54,140
Eliminating evil completely
is indeed my wish.

171
00:09:56,370 --> 00:09:57,410
But...

172
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,280
Do we have to meet here?

173
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,510
It's so dark here,

174
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,600
making us look like

175
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,660
we're plotting something sinister.

176
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:08,850
Master Puzhu dislikes crowded places.

177
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:10,360
The deeper one is in darkness,

178
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,200
the more one craves for light.

179
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:15,830
With enemies at our doorstep,

180
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,100
if the Sword Alliance
needs anything in the future,

181
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,760
just send someone to inform me.

182
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,380
I will go to Wanhua Hall

183
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,840
to discuss matters with you.

184
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,390
Great.

185
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:23,930
I never expected

186
00:10:24,020 --> 00:10:25,690
Master Puzhu to be

187
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:28,180
someone who knows how to be flexible.

188
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,490
To raid Fengliu Shop's strongholds,

189
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:39,620
I'll lead by example

190
00:10:40,190 --> 00:10:41,250
and go ahead first.

191
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:43,750
Perfect.

192
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:45,550
Deputy Lord Yu

193
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,870
has just arrived at the Sword Alliance
with his people.

194
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,870
I'll go with you to see him.

195
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,360
Master Puzhu,

196
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,450
is it really so unbearable for you

197
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:55,790
to work alongside me?

198
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,910
I've heard

199
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,920
that the disciples
of the Tianjing Pavilion

200
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:02,200
must practice meditation and tolerance.

201
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,670
How is it

202
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:05,040
that you don't need to practice these?

203
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,520
Farewell. Farewell.

204
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:14,570
I wish you good luck on your journey.

205
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,020
If Master Cheng

206
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,600
also wants to talk about

207
00:11:24,950 --> 00:11:26,190
approval

208
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:27,410
or other clichés,

209
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,750
I already know it.

210
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,000
Perhaps you do have the skills

211
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,870
to fight against the Fengliu Shop.

212
00:11:33,870 --> 00:11:35,390
But with your personality,

213
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,790
you can't inherit
the Seven‑String True Tune

214
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,790
of Fang Zhou.

215
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,080
Fang Zhou

216
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,610
was a man of integrity,

217
00:11:48,090 --> 00:11:49,120
but in the end,

218
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,240
apart from people's respect,

219
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,410
what else did he get?

220
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,120
Asking such a question shows

221
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:01,250
you don't understand
Fang Zhou well enough.

222
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:03,400
I don't want to be Fang Zhou.

223
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:05,290
You can't be him either.

224
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,240
You're suspected of being Yique Yinyang.

225
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,790
Though after the battle at Biluo Palace,

226
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:22,690
this suspicion was temporarily dispelled,

227
00:12:22,690 --> 00:12:24,620
but with your methods and actions,

228
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:26,030
no one can guarantee

229
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,750
that you won't become the next

230
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:28,750
Yique Yinyang.

231
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,080
You are a threat

232
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,770
to the Sword Alliance.

233
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,270
Tang Lici.

234
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,560
I'll be watching you.

235
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:41,970
You asked me before

236
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:44,000
if I've ever killed the wrong person
with my sword.

237
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,860
Perhaps I have,

238
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,920
but I have no regrets.

239
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,370
For all my mistakes,

240
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,390
I will atone in hell.

241
00:12:56,210 --> 00:12:57,410
Why are you laughing?

242
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:02,630
Master Cheng, your words

243
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,870
sound so resolute.

244
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:04,870
Have you

245
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,930
moved yourself with your own speech?

246
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:07,920
However,

247
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:10,560
your desire to atone is one-sided.

248
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,250
Have you considered

249
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,160
whether those souls in hell

250
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,870
are willing to give you

251
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,270
a chance for redemption?

252
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:51,360
Mr. Tang.

253
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,330
Master Shao, you haven't slept all night.

254
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,690
The turmoil in the jianghu hasn't settled,

255
00:13:58,690 --> 00:14:00,620
making it impossible to rest easy.

256
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,800
Forgive my boldness,

257
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:08,490
are you and the owner of the Fengliu Shop
Liu Yan

258
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:11,210
disciples of the same master?

259
00:14:13,050 --> 00:14:14,780
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

260
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,720
was our senior.

261
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,150
Chief Fang Zhou of Zhoudi Tower

262
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,410
was a man of principle.

263
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,570
My master Jiangnan Feng and he

264
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:26,010
once fought fiercely at Tiandu Peak,

265
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:28,510
together resisting
Yique Yinyang's rebellion.

266
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:30,970
Mr. Tang,
since you've inherited his legacy

267
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,660
and are willing to join us,

268
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:35,760
you must also have the desire
to help the world.

269
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,120
But my purpose

270
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:39,120
has never been peace in the jianghu.

271
00:14:39,190 --> 00:14:40,720
That's not contradictory.

272
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,790
Didn't you once tell

273
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:44,080
Master Puzhu

274
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,790
that even those with different paths
can work together?

275
00:14:46,790 --> 00:14:48,720
As long as our current goals align,

276
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,480
why not journey together for a while?

277
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:52,150
Rest assured,
since we're traveling together,

278
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,120
I will handle

279
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:55,310
all Sword Alliance matters properly.

280
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:56,240
However,

281
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:58,150
my methods in the future

282
00:14:58,270 --> 00:15:00,550
may be even more unacceptable
to ordinary people.

283
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,080
You

284
