Ms. Zhong.

869
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,180
Come with me to a place.

870
00:38:48,590 --> 00:38:49,120
Let's go.

871
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,920
The food is ready.

872
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:58,050
And the wine is here.

873
00:38:58,400 --> 00:39:00,190
Did you twist your ankle, Miss Shei?

874
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:00,920
Take it easy.

875
00:39:01,630 --> 00:39:02,320
Ms. Zhong.

876
00:39:06,730 --> 00:39:07,230
Zhong.

877
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,030
Ms. Zhong.

878
00:39:13,510 --> 00:39:14,510
Everyone's here.

879
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,400
Why are you so late?

880
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,590
We've been waiting for you
for a long time.

881
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:22,590
Shen and I finished our lessons ages ago.

882
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:24,430
Those Sword Masters
kept asking us questions.

883
00:39:24,430 --> 00:39:25,270
They asked me.

884
00:39:25,290 --> 00:39:27,150
You couldn't explain it clearly.

885
00:39:29,030 --> 00:39:29,630
Ms. Zhong,

886
00:39:30,050 --> 00:39:30,980
