887
00:39:31,340 --> 00:39:32,340
Come, have a seat.

888
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,670
Ms. Zhong, you stood up for justice,

889
00:39:42,050 --> 00:39:47,210
♪ Did you ever wonder then ♪

890
00:39:42,670 --> 00:39:44,270
yet you were punished for it.

891
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:44,920
I

892
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:47,280
feel it's completely unfair for you.

893
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:51,810
♪ As night quietly fell, to ask the moon ♪

894
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,520
But don't worry.

895
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,550
When we battle against the Fengliu Shop,

896
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,730
Yanmen Sect will lead the charge,

897
00:39:51,730 --> 00:39:52,960
and you'll definitely have a chance
to prove yourself.

898
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:57,150
♪ When the next dawn comes ♪

899
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:55,190
That's right, Zhong.

900
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:55,920
Take it easy.

901
00:39:56,490 --> 00:39:57,730
I believe you can do it.

902
00:39:57,730 --> 00:40:01,820
♪ Will we too be forgotten? ♪

903
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,110
Everyone

904
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:03,230
will help you return
to the Shanfeng Branch.

905
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:06,810
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

906
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:07,440
Then

907
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:11,730
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

908
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:09,390
thank you all.

909
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,760
Thank you, Master Jiang.

910
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:17,460
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

911
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:15,440
Thank you,

912
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:17,280
Mr. Tang.

913
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:22,160
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

914
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:19,960
Ms. Zhong,

915
00:40:20,190 --> 00:40:21,250
no need for thanks.

916
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:22,240
Fengliu Shop

917
00:40:22,550 --> 00:40:24,110
tricked my son into taking the Evil Pill.

918
00:40:22,970 --> 00:40:27,320
♪ The sunlight falls upon you ♪

919
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,460
If it weren't for Ms. Zhong

920
00:40:26,550 --> 00:40:27,550
and everyone else

921
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:28,840
helping me expose the traitor,

922
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:32,000
♪ Just like when you asked me back then ♪

923
00:40:30,150 --> 00:40:31,880
Yanmen Sect would be in danger.

924
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,260
Both officially and personally,

925
00:40:33,260 --> 00:40:37,670
♪ How do we hide certain answers ♪

926
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,510
I should help you.

927
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:37,020
Let's not talk about this now.

928
00:40:37,690 --> 00:40:42,980
♪ Those burning moments with you? ♪

929
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:40,160
Let's enjoy this brief moment of peace.

930
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:41,960
What wine did you bring, Jiang?

931
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:44,630
This is the finest wine from Yanmen.

932
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:46,230
Frosty Leaves' Red.

933
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:48,650
A Yanmen specialty, excellent wine.

934
00:40:48,890 --> 00:40:50,760
Paired with Shei's delicious dishes,

935
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:53,030
there is wine and food. Let me try first.

936
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:53,760
Chi,

937
00:40:54,370 --> 00:40:56,170
don't start eating by yourself.

938
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,360
I...

939
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:58,800
It's alright.

940
00:40:59,040 --> 00:41:01,330
Today is a family gathering;
no need for formalities.

941
00:41:01,330 --> 00:41:02,990
Everyone, let's have a toast.

942
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:08,700
♪ The northern wind hums by my ear ♪

943
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,130
Cheers.

944
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:13,180
♪ Stirring waves between your brows ♪

945
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:18,960
♪ The flowers scatter in June ♪

946
00:41:19,160 --> 00:41:23,240
♪ I'd rather jump into your soil ♪

947
00:41:24,230 --> 00:41:24,880
Ms. Zhong.

948
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,250
Are you unhappy?

949
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:29,190
No.

950
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:31,000
I just feel

951
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:33,330
that it feels like ages

952
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:35,320
since I last saw everyone.

953
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:38,150
The last time we went to Sword King City

954
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:40,480
seems like it happened in a previous life.

955
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:44,670
I'd like to toast everyone.

956
00:41:45,550 --> 00:41:46,830
No matter how much time passes,

957
00:41:46,830 --> 00:41:48,690
we should always drink together.

958
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:50,290
You always know what to say.

959
00:42:16,330 --> 00:42:18,530
You seem very happy tonight, Ms. Zhong.

960
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,180
Why is it you again?

961
00:42:21,590 --> 00:42:22,710
Do you need something?

962
00:42:22,710 --> 00:42:23,760
I asked you first.

963
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,840
So you should answer me first.

964
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:27,430
Of course I'm happy.

965
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:28,960
Your turn.

966
00:42:29,220 --> 00:42:30,440
I don't have anything specific.

967
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:30,880
Why?

968
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:33,490
Can't I chat with you without a reason?

969
00:42:36,310 --> 00:42:37,790
You're so strange.

970
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:39,760
If you came to the Sword Alliance

971
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,090
with other intentions,

972
00:42:41,250 --> 00:42:42,250
I suggest

973
00:42:43,140 --> 00:42:44,420
you leave now.

974
00:42:45,510 --> 00:42:46,970
You're quite perceptive.

975
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:48,230
Fine.

976
00:42:48,590 --> 00:42:49,390
I'll tell you.

977
00:42:49,990 --> 00:42:51,480
I came to the Sword Alliance

978
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,960
to see

979
00:42:53,150 --> 00:42:55,110
the true face of the fox demon.

980
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:57,590
Why?

981
00:42:58,260 --> 00:42:58,820
Why?

982
00:43:00,030 --> 00:43:00,760
Because...

983
00:43:01,690 --> 00:43:04,290
Mr. Tang is indeed detestable and hateful,

984
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:05,960
but I must admit

985
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:09,000
that he does have a captivating charm.

986
00:43:09,550 --> 00:43:11,150
It makes one unable to resist

987
00:43:11,510 --> 00:43:13,000
falling deeply for him.

988
00:43:16,670 --> 00:43:18,280
You dare to provoke Mr. Tang?

989
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:21,510
Aren't you afraid
that you'll bring disaster upon yourself?

990
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:23,880
It's the danger that makes it attractive.

991
00:43:24,230 --> 00:43:24,880
You

992
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:27,210
understand this feeling best, don't you?

993
00:43:29,150 --> 00:43:31,240
What are you talking about?

994
00:43:32,670 --> 00:43:34,280
What I want to say is,

995
00:43:34,740 --> 00:43:35,960
to get his attention,

996
00:43:36,520 --> 00:43:38,520
you can't follow the ordinary path.

997
00:43:39,630 --> 00:43:41,760
You need to be the most special person.

998
00:43:42,280 --> 00:43:43,920
Don't let yourself need him;

999
00:43:44,290 --> 00:43:46,690
make him need you instead.

1000
00:43:48,380 --> 00:43:50,300
What's between Mr. Tang and me

1001
00:43:50,960 --> 00:43:52,480
is none of your business.

1002
00:43:54,430 --> 00:43:55,510
To be honest,

1003
00:43:55,710 --> 00:43:57,240
I've read your fortune too.

1004
00:43:58,200 --> 00:44:00,840
Your destiny shows weak family bonds

1005
00:44:01,110 --> 00:44:02,510
and no power or wealth.

1006
00:44:03,030 --> 00:44:04,630
What others are born with,

1007
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:06,230
you must fight desperately to obtain—

1008
00:44:06,230 --> 00:44:08,630
only then might you stand a slim chance
of getting it.

1009
00:44:08,630 --> 00:44:10,490
If you miss just one opportunity,

1010
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:13,320
you'll lose everything.

1011
00:44:19,070 --> 00:44:20,440
Mr. Fang, do you think

1012
00:44:20,730 --> 00:44:22,260
I would believe your words?

1013
00:44:22,580 --> 00:44:24,170
It doesn't matter if you don't.

1014
00:44:24,170 --> 00:44:25,230
But if I were you,

1015
00:44:25,230 --> 00:44:26,440
with such a fate,

1016
00:44:26,540 --> 00:44:27,480
I would contentedly

1017
00:44:27,480 --> 00:44:28,880
be an ordinary disciple

1018
00:44:29,590 --> 00:44:31,320
and marry a simple, honest man.

1019
00:44:32,110 --> 00:44:33,370
Why struggle for more?

1020
00:44:34,590 --> 00:44:36,320
What if I insist on struggling?

1021
00:44:40,480 --> 00:44:41,960
Then I can help you.

1022
00:44:48,460 --> 00:44:49,320
I don't need it.

1023
00:44:53,820 --> 00:44:54,920
Think carefully,

1024
00:44:55,300 --> 00:44:56,170
Ms. Zhong.

1025
00:45:25,240 --> 00:45:26,770
A letter from Shisan Tower.

1026
00:45:27,340 --> 00:45:29,650
The Peach of Three Hues in Pink Attire.

1027
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:32,190
She is Xifang Tao.

1028
00:45:53,490 --> 00:45:55,350
Hand it to Godfather personally.

1029
00:45:56,160 --> 00:45:57,370
Bring back his reply.

1030
00:45:59,690 --> 00:46:02,020
Aren't you going
to ask what this is about?

1031
00:46:03,220 --> 00:46:05,080
I don't have Chi Yun's curiosity.

1032
00:46:05,630 --> 00:46:06,630
The more you know,

1033
00:46:07,030 --> 00:46:08,090
the sooner you die.

1034
00:46:18,370 --> 00:46:19,210
Sometimes,

1035
00:46:20,100 --> 00:46:21,320
the more you know,

1036
00:46:21,880 --> 00:46:23,280
the better your chances.

1037
00:46:24,280 --> 00:46:25,320
Fang Pingzhai,

1038
00:46:25,840 --> 00:46:27,000
your true identity

1039
00:46:27,000 --> 00:46:28,480
is about to be revealed.

